{"tid":1049014,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[國民心碎] (G)I-DLE編舞「舒華完全被擋30秒」！","createTime":"2019-03-06T03:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T17:49:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"88eb762789473a2e51caabb7e9672f387c28afa0","tid":1049014,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3936/d3936220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3936%2Fd3936220.jpg&h=2ac4ff52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲(G)I-DLE正以新專輯回歸樂壇。（圖／翻攝自(G)I-DLE臉書）<br />\n<br />\n隊形編排單調，走位缺乏新意<br />\n6人團體若要抓住中心點並顯得對稱，經常會使用「2-1-2-1」來變化隊形。然而，此種排列之缺陷，在於中心點必須重疊，因此最後一排的成員會完全被遮蔽。但在〈LATATA〉中，下圖兩種「2-1-2-1」隊形居然涵蓋超過全曲一半的分量；換言之，6人全部呈現在觀眾眼前的時間其實非常短暫，經常有人會被前排成員擋住。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3936/d3936141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3936%2Fd3936141.jpg&h=7e433d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲(G)I-DLE「2-1-2-1隊形排列」。（圖／翻攝自CUBE官方YouTube頻道）<br />\n<br />\n〈LATATA〉作為(G)I-DLE的起點，因為沒有其他作品可供比較，進而缺乏討論空間。但是緊接著，在第二次回歸的〈HANN(Alone)〉中，除了先前大量使用的「2-1-2-1」外，副歌更全部運用「1-2-2-1」隊形。同時，四個八拍被擋住的成員都是美延，意即在歌曲最重要的段落，乍看之下卻像是五人團體，美延居然完全沒有亮相。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3936/d3936143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3936%2Fd3936143.jpg&h=3c663a38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲(G)I-DLE「1-2-2-1隊形」。（圖／翻攝自CUBE官方YouTube頻道）<br />\n<br />\n其實，「1-2-2-1」隊形也常見於其他六人女團中，例如<strong>Apin</strong>k的〈I'm so sick〉副歌前半段，恩地雖與普美重疊，但時間僅有兩個八拍；同時副歌後段是由恩地負責，如此編排還增加了些許登場的驚喜感。而恩地身為團體主唱，存在感本就相當強烈，因此舞台並不會因這樣的編排失衡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3936/d3936146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3936%2Fd3936146.jpg&h=7486345c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲同樣為6人女團的Apink編舞，重疊部分較少。（圖／翻攝自Apink官方YouTube頻道）<br />\n<br />\n另一組六人女團是<strong>GFRIEND</strong>，〈LOVE WHISPER〉副歌幾乎全部使用「1-2-2-1」的隊形，一直都有成員與中心點重合；然而她們採用二個八拍走位一次的方式，讓前後成員皆有所交換，被遮住的成員並非固定一人，因此顯得較為平均且流動性強。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BryESQvnfoc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBryESQvnfoc&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=ce76beb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BryESQvnfoc</a><br />\n<br />\n只要是六人女團，就一定有人被擋住嗎？我想<strong>AOA</strong>〈Bingle Bangle〉的編排是一個優秀範例。歌曲中，舞蹈動線幾乎沒有人被遮擋，所有人都獲得非常完整的表現空間，隊形也能走出許多新花樣。（再說AOA也不是一開始就6人，是經過快速調整後的結果。）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l1aV_N-mBQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl1aV_N-mBQ4&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=68f00d78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l1aV_N-mBQ4</a><br />\n<br />\n從目前音樂節目的舞台表現而言，小娟與穗珍明顯較其他團員更游刃有餘。與其說二人真的實力超群太多，不如說是因為其他團員尚未有適當機會進行潛能開發。<br />\n<br />\n一個團體中若人氣、份量極度不均會有什麼後果？公司CUBE早已有切身經驗。然而，若(G)I-DLE仍以如此步伐前行，不禁令人感到可惜──因為她們絕對有實力更上一層樓，不該僅止於此。因此，在人才輩出、競爭激烈的偶像世界裡，如何掌握自身的優勢及定位，是(G)I-DLE與CUBE在現階段，必須嚴肅思考的課題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3936/d3936207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3936%2Fd3936207.jpg&h=0ef7decd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲(G)I-DLE新曲〈Senorita〉後方舒華直接被擋30秒。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／1theK (원더케이)）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_DlaP6PbxQM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_DlaP6PbxQM&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=c493c269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_DlaP6PbxQM</a>"},{"pid":"fb7ae39096208400a5c72482050492b07f5602dd","tid":1049014,"uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3935/3935473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3935%2F3935473.jpg&h=02853b83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8699f900090335e41194a01dca9d00cd4ef83318","tid":1049014,"uid":213300,"like":35,"dislike":10,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"我之前話撚咗佢啦<br />\n又唔退團<br />\n冇料又要霸住個位出道<br />\n根本佢自己都未準備好出道<br />\n宜家又唔撚知佢定位係咩<br />\n鳩吓鳩吓都唔知做乜柒"},{"pid":"468100c15fd0f867561bfa3d4a0cd06e0f6d7ead","tid":1049014,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:57:50.000Z","msg":"都唔知邊撚個編<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c681648bae0e580d67b8b018d7128cdd87fd4b10","tid":1049014,"uid":555,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8699f900090335e41194a01dca9d00cd4ef83318","tid":1049014,"uid":213300,"like":35,"dislike":10,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"我之前話撚咗佢啦<br />\n又唔退團<br />\n冇料又要霸住個位出道<br />\n根本佢自己都未準備好出道<br />\n宜家又唔撚知佢定位係咩<br />\n鳩吓鳩吓都唔知做乜柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"收啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"a330f92fb0077d6bf12fab88def9c5403834a4f3","tid":1049014,"uid":147770,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"舒華成首歌只係wo oh oh ~~~~"},{"pid":"66fce0521cf1706db30cb8cfed77cc1e8ff44290","tid":1049014,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"6人團編舞係咁上下"},{"pid":"4e3878f646ba70b9fe8ba0497ff4b4537a9c359d","tid":1049014,"uid":55013,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"隻舞好柒..<br />\n好似喺度捉蝨咁"},{"pid":"da75248f8236e9e002d742562e23b26a6bd06812","tid":1049014,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66fce0521cf1706db30cb8cfed77cc1e8ff44290","tid":1049014,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"6人團編舞係咁上下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"